definitions.definition: A farmer ; one who grows things.
examples: He was an orange grower from Florida.

definitions.definition: Someone or something, especially music , that becomes more likeable over time.
examples: I didn't like the song at first, but it is a real grower .

definitions.definition: A man whose penis increases in size significantly when erect .

main_definition: A farmer ; one who grows things.
secondary_definitions: Someone or something, especially music , that becomes more likeable over time. [from 1990s]
( slang ) A man whose penis increases in size significantly when erect . [from 1990s]
